{"tid":926772,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"尋日發左個夢 求解","createTime":"2018-12-03T16:39:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-03T23:51:20.000Z","uid":143371,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e9a66bb212272bf65d625f12eb7207fedd5d5e07","tid":926772,"uid":143371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T16:39:10.000Z","msg":"唔講咁多 直入正題。<br />\n<br />\n發夢手痕禁下手機銀行戶口有幾多錢，之前發覺比人禁走左8皮野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  即刻好驚慌<br />\n<br />\n之後即刻打比銀行，好合理地，係線路煩忙冇人聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後決定報警，點知屌佢老尾叫我sd email formal報比佢地。奇怪在我覆左話：哦要咁formal架？<br />\n<br />\n之後場景一轉，係屋企夜晚訓緊教，半夜竟然有人潛入我屋企 拎我部電腦，之後我發現左大叫邊個！點知佢拎左把唔知咩槍出黎射9暈我，之後就夢醒左。<br />\n<br />\n而尋日現實我真係有手機禁過銀行有幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個夢代表d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"389eb38adceb788617b7aed8ea4da204d6caa6f9","tid":926772,"uid":140145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T16:40:20.000Z","msg":"日有所思 夜有所夢"},{"pid":"8d27fd7807466d8b3ec15697849f15d78b8864da","tid":926772,"uid":43924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T17:03:57.000Z","msg":"利申：銀行户口得8舊水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68481622715ab79d897edbbdc81452ae0091610d","tid":926772,"uid":199211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T17:09:13.000Z","msg":"部電過八皮野"},{"pid":"3eb561813595e138ed4345045e5c7d95f8a8e024","tid":926772,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T17:32:48.000Z","msg":"平時你諗開咩，夜晚就發返相關嘅夢。你現實入面一定有啲珍而重之嘅野，好驚俾人偷？"},{"pid":"2e6c959a05558602113467875f7667ca18c3a4a4","tid":926772,"uid":143371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3eb561813595e138ed4345045e5c7d95f8a8e024","tid":926772,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T17:32:48.000Z","msg":"平時你諗開咩，夜晚就發返相關嘅夢。你現實入面一定有啲珍而重之嘅野，好驚俾人偷？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T23:51:20.000Z","msg":"可能因為前排出糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}